IDLE RPM

Idle RPM is an idle/clicker racing game inspired by Cookie Clicker, built for players who want something fun to grind in short bursts without committing hours to a full playthrough.
Upgrade your car, enter increasingly competitive races, and climb the motorsport ladder from grassroots leagues all the way to Formula 1.
------------------------------------------------
Problem Description

Many players have free time but donâ€™t want to start a large, time consuming game. They want something engaging, rewarding, and easy to jump in and out of.
Idle RPM solves this by combining idle progression with active clicking and racing strategy.
------------------------------------------------
Target Audience

Casual gamers
Fans of idle games
Racing and car enthusiasts
Players who enjoy progression and upgrades
